<!--
Sprint 62.5 B4: Codex code_sign_clone GC LaunchAgent (2026-06-22)

痛点: Codex app 每次更新做 code_sign_clone 复制到
  /private/var/folders/tz/<user>/X/com.openai.codex.code_sign_clone.*/
  累积 40 份 = 53GB. 2026-06-22 磁盘急救时清理 (释放 ~52GB).

治根: 每天凌晨 03:00 跑 GC, 删 > 7 天的 clone, 保留最新 1 份 (Codex 启动时
  可能仍需要的最新 Gatekeeper clone).

复用 com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist 模式 (Sprint 4 P0-2) +
  Sprint 60.2 P3 L4.7 永久规则 (launchd 启动器首选 python3 不用 bash).

设计:
  - Label: com.local.codex-clone-gc
  - ProgramArguments: python3 + codex_clone_gc.py (避开 macOS sandbox deny bash)
  - WorkingDirectory: 主仓根
  - StartCalendarInterval: 03:00 daily (跟 backup 不冲突, backup 03:30)
  - 不 KeepAlive (单次跑完退出)
  - StandardOutPath + StandardErrorPath: /tmp/fuqing-codex-clone-gc.log

安装:
  cp scripts/launchd/com.local.codex-clone-gc.plist ~/Library/LaunchAgents/
  launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.local.codex-clone-gc.plist 2>/dev/null
  launchctl load -w ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.local.codex-clone-gc.plist
  launchctl list | grep codex-clone-gc   验证加载

卸载:
  launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.local.codex-clone-gc.plist
  rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.local.codex-clone-gc.plist
-->
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>Label</key>
    <string>com.local.codex-clone-gc</string>

    <key>ProgramArguments</key>
    <array>
        <string>/Users/hutou/homebrew/bin/python3</string>
        <string>/Users/hutou/Desktop/fuqin-date/fuqing-crm-analytics/scripts/launchd/codex_clone_gc.py</string>
    </array>

    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>
    <string>/Users/hutou/Desktop/fuqin-date/fuqing-crm-analytics</string>

    <key>StartCalendarInterval</key>
    <dict>
        <key>Hour</key>
        <integer>3</integer>
        <key>Minute</key>
        <integer>0</integer>
    </dict>

    <key>StandardOutPath</key>
    <string>/tmp/fuqing-codex-clone-gc.log</string>

    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
    <string>/tmp/fuqing-codex-clone-gc.log</string>

    <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>
    <dict>
        <key>PATH</key>
        <string>/Users/hutou/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin</string>
    </dict>
</dict>
</plist>